HEADWORD: Pledgor
<hw>Pledg*or"</hw> }</mhw> <pr>(?)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>One who pledges, or delivers
anything in pledge; a pledger; -- opposed to
<ant>pledgee</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
